*******************************************************************************
       Name: Oathshield
       Kind: Skill
     Target: TAR_CHAR_DEFENSIVE (other)
   Position: POS_FIGHTING
   Min Mana: 0
 Wait Beats: 24
 Can Learn: TRUE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: The oathshield fades.
Acquisition:
   - Templar: level 10
Description:
   Oathshield extends the Templar's oath to shield an ally, granting them
   an AC bonus for several rounds. This represents the Solar Court
   auxiliaries' threshold-guardian role -- standing between danger and
   those they protect.

   Target: Must target another character (cannot self-cast)
   Costs: Movement (via subtract_energy_cost)
   Cooldown: 20 rounds
   Duration: 3 + (Templar level / 5) rounds
   AC modifier: -(Templar level * 4 + Paladin level * 2)

   This is the only ally-targeted defensive buff in the adept system,
   reflecting the Templar's unique position as both combatant and protector.
*******************************************************************************
